direction: right

Title: Signal Conditioning Flow {class: adi-title}

Hardware Setup: {
  class: adi-container

  ADC: {
    shape: class
    class: adi-ADC
    width: 150
    height: 80
  }
  
  Filter: {
    shape: class
    class: adi-filter
    width: 150
    height: 80
  }

  DAC: {
    shape: class
    class: adi-DAC
    width: 150
    height: 80
  }
  
  OpAmp: {
    shape: class
    class: adi-amp
    width: 150
    height: 80
  }
}

Sensor -> Hardware Setup.OpAmp: Analog Signal {class: adi-signal-analog}
Hardware Setup.OpAmp -> Hardware Setup.ADC: Amplified {class: adi-signal-analog}
Hardware Setup.ADC -> Hardware Setup.Filter: Digitize {class: adi-signal-digital}
Hardware Setup.Filter -> Hardware Setup.DAC: Clean Signal {class: adi-signal-digital}
Hardware Setup.DAC -> Actuator: Output {class: adi-signal-analog}

Clock -> Hardware Setup.ADC: 10MHz {class: adi-signal-clock}
Clock -> Hardware Setup.DAC: 10MHz {class: adi-signal-clock}

Note: Ensure strict clock synchronicity across conversions. {class: adi-note}
